Text: hey me again, do you have any cd's by Foolish Things? they quit a couple years ago but never got there last cd. God Bless

Super1313, after a quick internet search today, I may be wrong, but I think Foolish Things has only released three albums.  I have two of the three, and am just missing their first 2002 self titled album.  So I put up a quick 2-disc discography for you. Have fun! :)
Great work. I think I asked you before but did you find any Jahaziel albums. Thanks again

PooterP551, my apologies about Jahaziel. I thought I responded already. None the less, I think Jahaziel only has two albums released. And I only have one of the two, which hardly makes for a "discography." That's the bad news. The good news is you can still download the album which I do have. Do a search for 2011 Year In Christian Music, specifically the 7th Bundle. There you will find his "The Still Livin' Mixtape" for immediate download today.
